modName: Lady of Death - UNPB BBP - FavoredSoul
summary: A conversion of the Lady of Death Set by newermind43 for UNPB-BBP and FavoredSoul bodies with working weight slider.
descriptionHtml:
A conversion of the Lady of Death Set by newermind43 for UNPB-BBP and FavoredSoul bodies with working weight slider.

English is not my native language so sorry for my mistakes.


Female version
=============
Required mods:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13761]Lady of Death Set for CBBE V3[/url]
The UNPB body replacer with BBP support: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37900/]UNPB REDUX PROJECT[/url] OR [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20227/?]Troublemakers Clothing[/url]
Make sure you install a BBP package or the chest piece will CTD your game.


Male version
===========
Required mod:
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488]Better males - Beautiful nudes and faces - New hairstyles[/url] FavoredSoul meshes
Notes:
I have converted only the main armor, so no corset, boots, etc


Installation
=========
First install the required mods
Use NMM and overwrite when asked.
Manual installation: open archive, extract meshes folder into data folder and overwrite when asked.


Credits and thanks
================
newermind43 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13761]Lady of Death Set for CBBE V3[/url]
calyps and xp32 and mrtroublemaker for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899]UNP BLESSED BODY UNPB - With Optional BBP Breast Physics[/url]
dimon99 for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]
Chris57 and FavoredSoul for [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488]Better males - Beautiful nudes and faces - New hairstyles[/url]
